{
  "text": "The nucleotide to protein (N/P) ratio of 1.85 obtained from the ratio of optical density at 260 and 280 nm (A 260 /A 280 = 1.85) was taken as evidence for protein free DNA [CITATION_1] . Stock solution of AMC (6 mM) was prepared by dissolving AMC in 10% aqueous methanol.",
